===============================
 How to install Photo Engine X
===============================

REQUIRED SOFTWARE

- openresty (nginx+lua)
- redis
- imagemagick convert utility

REQUIRED PACKAGES

- python-pyexiv2
- python-redis    
- python-pythonmagick

PREPARATIONS

- Set $INSTALL_ROOT/img/ folder writable by webserver user.
- Check out submodules using: git submodule update --init
- Bootstrap css needs to be downloaded seperately or generated using 
  their provided makefile
- Copy $INSTALL_ROOT/etc/config.json.dist to $INSTALL_ROOT/etc/config.json and
  update to reflect your settings

